2.6 Comments

Regular Comments

Regular comments use /* */ syntax and can be nested.

```pascal
/* This is a comment */

/* This comment
   spans multiple
   lines */

/* Comments can /* nest */ safely */
```

Documentation Comments

Documentation comments use /// syntax for single-line and block documentation.

```pascal
/// This is a documentation comment
function add(a: int32, b: int32): int32

///
/// This is a block documentation comment
/// that spans multiple lines
/// 
/// @param a The first number
/// @param b The second number
/// @return The sum of a and b
///
function subtract(a: int32, b: int32): int32
```

Comment Rules Summary

Type Syntax Nesting Purpose
Regular comment /* ... */ Yes Implementation notes, TODOs, disabled code
Documentation comment /// ... No API documentation
Block documentation ///\n/// ...\n/// No Multi-line API documentation

