Part 9: Memory Management

9.1 Ownership System

```pascal
var a: own string := "hello"
var b: ref string := &a   /* borrow */
var c: mut string := &mut a  /* mutable borrow */
var d: own string := consume a  /* move */
/* a is now invalid */
```

9.2 Compile-Time Reference Counting

```pascal
var a: rc string := "shared"   /* refcount = 1 */
var b: rc string := a           /* refcount = 2 */
var c: rc string := a           /* refcount = 3 */
var weak: weak string := a      /* weak reference */
```

9.3 Explicit Allocators

```pascal
var arena := Arena.init(alloc)
var data := arena.alloc(u8, 1024)
defer arena.deinit()
```

9.4 Defer Statement

```pascal
var file := File.open("data.txt")
defer file.close()
```

