## Part 15: Compiler Implementation

### 15.1 Backends

| Architecture | Status | Output Format |
|--------------|--------|---------------|
| x86_64 | ✅ | ELF, Mach-O, PE |
| ARM64 | ✅ | ELF, Mach-O, PE |
| RISC-V | ✅ | ELF |
| WebAssembly | ✅ | WASM |

### 15.2 Self-Hosting

The Maia compiler is self-hosted:
1. Stage 0: Zig compiler (bootstrap)
2. Stage 1: Maia compiler (compiled by Zig)
3. Stage 2: Maia compiler (compiled by Stage 1)

